rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1591:"<p><a href="http://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/logo-wysija-600px.png"><img class="size-medium wp-image-292 alignright" title="logo-wysija-600px" src="http://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/logo-wysija-600px-300x111.png" alt="" width="300" height="111" /></a>Coming Soon Pro Version 3.5.0 has been released.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Changes:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Added WYSIJA provider</li>\n<li>Initialize class in init hook to avoid conflicts</li>\n<li>Added the ability to delete individual subscribers.</li>\n<li>Rearranged subscriber table and added sort options and referrer links</li>\n<li>Display the subscriber referrer url if they are already subscribed and resubmitted the front end form.</li>\n<li>Expire the client view immediately when removed.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/wysija-newsletters/" target="_blank">WYSIJA</a> lets you create newsletters, post notifications and autoresponders. Drag and drop your posts, images, social icons. Pick one of 20 themes. Change fonts and colors on the fly. Configuration is dummy proof. A complete email solution for WordPress. Finally.</p>\n<p>Learn more about <a href="http://www.wysija.com/" target="_blank">WYSIJA</a>. Look for the demo video soon&#8230;</p>\n<p>You should receive an automatic upgrade notification within 12hrs.</p>\n<p>The post <a href="http://www.seedprod.com/coming-soon-pro-version-3-5-0-release-with-wysija-integration/">Coming Soon Pro Version 3.5.0 Release with WYSIJA Integration</a> appeared first on <a href="http://www.seedprod.com">SeedProd</a>.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:91:"http://www.seedprod.com/coming-soon-pro-version-3-5-0-release-with-wysija-integration/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_ba